  ;; ========================================================================
  ;; CLOCK GENERATION
  ;; ========================================================================
  ;; Y1: 100MHz TCXO (SiT5356AI) → FPGA reference clock input
  ;; U20: Si5395A PLL synthesizer (QFN-28)
  ;;   Input: 100MHz from Y1
  ;;   Output 0: 2.0 GHz → CLK_HBM (NCE HBM5 controller)
  ;;   Output 1: 156.25 MHz → CLK_SERDES (TFLN SerDes reference)
  ;;   Output 2: 200 MHz → spare
  ;; ========================================================================

